The last topic I really I don't have time for this but I'm gonna do it anyway, it's just such an important topic

00:22:18.719 --> 00:22:24.239
Tool calling allows LLMs to interact with other systems. So instead of just taking text in and

00:22:25.280 --> 00:22:31.079
Giving text back out. It gives the LLMs the ability to call out to

00:22:32.439 --> 00:22:38.119
APIs to databases the ability to execute code to do things to your file system

