So another way to think of it is that the client can do things that the assistant can't do like

00:26:08.260 --> 00:26:12.099
not only call out to things like a weather service, but

00:26:12.739 --> 00:26:19.739
To read and write to databases to put files on disk to turn the lights on and off in a smart home

00:26:20.060 --> 00:26:21.819
Anything you can think of doing in code

00:26:21.819 --> 00:26:27.020
You can empower the assistant to do and we put the control into the hands of the assistant

00:26:27.020 --> 00:26:33.219
so that the assistant can decide when it's appropriate to use what tools and what arguments to pass in and

00:26:33.459 --> 00:26:37.020
What to do with the results and it turns out that that's just an incredibly

00:26:37.699 --> 00:26:39.699
general and powerful

00:26:39.739 --> 00:26:45.380
Capability having that intelligence in using and coordinating these tools

